 《绝命毒师》的房子正在出售https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-writing-bad-house-is-up-for-sale-3826029?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-writing-bad-house-is-up-出售Laura MolloySat, 04 Jan 2025 10:46:32 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3826029 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于粉丝流量高，现任车主在 52 年后出售，称他们平均“每天 300 辆车”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-breaking-bad-house-is-up-for-sale-3826029">《绝命毒师》的房子正在出售的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-home-for-the-White-residence-in-‘Breaking-Bad-located-in-Albuquerque-New-Mexico.-CREDIT_-Steve-Snowden_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/breaking-bad"><em>《绝命毒师》的</em></a>房子现在正在出售。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/better-call-saul-season-7-breaking-bad-universe-3287396">《绝命毒师》宇宙的下一步是什么？</a></strong></li></ul><p>这座房子位于新墨西哥州阿尔伯克基，在 2008 年至 2013 年播出的由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bryan-cranston">布莱恩·科兰斯顿 (Bryan Cranston)</a>主演的连续剧中，被用作沃尔特·怀特 (Walter White) 的家。</p><p>该房屋的市场售价为 400 万美元（320 万英镑），尽管该地区其他类似房屋的估价为 35 万美元（281,746 英镑）。</p><p>节目自开播以来，粉丝们纷纷前往现场拍照。据<a href="https://consequence.net/2025/01/breaking-bad-house-for-sale/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Consequence</em></a>报道，现任车主 Joanne Quintana 在接受当地广播电台 KOB4 采访时表示，他们平均“每天 300 辆汽车”。</p><p>尽管金塔纳回忆起了该剧制作中的一些积极回忆，包括克兰斯顿一次把披萨扔到屋顶上的那一天，但她告诉电视台，她对近年来粉丝的流量以及那些重现该剧的人感到沮丧。著名的披萨时刻。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《绝命毒师》- 屋顶披萨场景 (S3E2) |烂番茄电视" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6vvJ26Nr3KI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>最近，他们添加了围栏来保护财产，但 52 年后的现在，他们选择离开。 “我们将带着我们的回忆离开。是时候继续前进了。我们完成了。没有理由再打架了，”金塔纳说。 “我希望他们能做到球迷想要的那样。他们想要一个民宿，他们想要一个博物馆，他们想要进入它。大胆试试吧。”</p><p>去年，克兰斯顿 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/bryan-cranston-tells-breaking-bad-fans-to-let-it-go-3578529">告诉<em>《绝命毒师》</em>粉丝，是时候让这部剧结束了</a>，他解释说：“一切都应该结束。一切都是循环的。我们的生活是循环的。季节，树木，一切。所以，有一个开始、中间和结尾，然后就可以了。我为我们所做的事情感到自豪。”</p><p>除了在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/better-call-saul"><em>《风骚律师》</em></a>最后一季中客串外，克兰斯顿还在 2019 年的一次性电影<em>《El Camino》</em>中以怀特的身份短暂露面，并在 2023 年的超级碗广告中复活了该角色。</p><p>创作者文斯·吉利根还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/vince-gilligan-discusses-chances-of-breaking-bad-spin-off-about-walt-jr-3510550">讨论了 2023 年为怀特的儿子小沃尔特 (RJ Mitte) 制作衍生剧的可能性</a>。</p><p>其他新闻方面，去年<em>《绝命毒师》</em>在<em>烂番茄</em>上的一项粉丝投票中被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/this-is-the-best-tv-show-of-the-past-25-years-according-to-fans-3501799">评为过去 25 年最佳节目</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-breaking-bad-house-is-up-for-sale-3826029">《绝命毒师》的房子正在出售的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
